show.description: Gussa, gareebi aur gairat — jab teeno takraate hain, toh aag lagti hai! Sharon se apna paisa chhinnne nikla John, lekin saamne mila ek system jo sirf dar dikhata hai. Dekhiye kaise ek aadmi, pura khel palat deta hai.
